Notes:
- Files are tab-separated (chapter, verse, text), one verse per line,
  named after the Latin Vulgate book names, matching the format of the
  douay-rheims/, aelf/, and matos-soares/ folders. Generated by
  ../extract-swahili.js from the USFM source (unzip swhonen_usfm.zip
  into swahili/src/ to regenerate).
- This translation uses the Protestant canon: the deuterocanonical books
  (Sapientia, Ecclesiasticus, Tobiæ, Judith, Baruch, Machabæorum 1-2)
  are not included, so readings from those books will not display in
  Swahili.
- Psalmi.txt uses the Hebrew (Masoretic) psalm numbering, not the
  Vulgate numbering used elsewhere on this site.
